summary:
Very enthusiastic and committed all-round Petrophysicist, who enjoys working and collaborating in multi-cultural, multi-disciplinary teams. Experienced in interpreting reservoir properties in gas and oil wells, in clastic & limestone reservoirs and shale deposits. Extensive experience with working in and leading integrated subsurface teams. Hands-on experience in log and core (data) acquisition, liaison with contractors and core laboratories. Experienced in setting-up and running full-field petrophysical data models, including full interpretation and application of routine and special core analysis data. Keen interest in and recent exposure to renewable energy (Geothermal) projects.
Skilled Microsoft DIY coach for PowerApps & PowerAutomate. Extensive knowledge of PowerBI
